Starstomp jumped in and used her jets to slow her fall. She readied 
her proton rifle, just in case.

Starstomp:
I wish these jets could do more than short bursts, that way I could 
have flied all the way down instead of falling... Anyways, I suggest 
we find our way to the bridge or to the CRs, that's where it'll be 
likely to find someone.
